name: map-service-showing-geology-oil-and-gas-fields-and-geological-provinces-of-the-former-soviet-un
notes: This map service includes geology, center points of oil and gas fields, geologic provinces, and political boundaries in the Former Soviet Union. This compilation is part of an interim product of the U.S. Geological Survey's World Energy Project (WEP) and part of a series on CD-ROM. The data sets were designed originally in ESRI's ARC/INFO ver. 7.0.4 and 7.1.2 system.
